pageContext.claim: “But I think that with few exceptions no president has done anywhere near what we've done in his first six months. Not even close.”
pageContext.analysis: This is wrong. Just among recent presidents, Jimmy Carter, George H.W. Bush and Bill Clinton had signed more bills than Trump at this point in their presidencies. Moreover, Trump has no signed no major legislation and most of his efforts are stuck in Congress or have not even been proposed yet.
